 of\nspectrophotometric properties which may ultimately be related to differences in\naccretion modes if high-luminosity quasars are considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jul 2018 09:25:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-10"}
